<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٦٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(لا تمن)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> الموت فإنك ميت، ولكن <span class="c2">(سل)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> اللَّه العافية <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
